		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have swapped H and G chips from time-to-time. They seem identical, I'd assume the major difference is process type and method; The H series seems to have a better matte finish on the chip...Then again, all the H chips I've worked with were the same batch 4BM 4V.

		

		</td>
