<br />
<br />Someone had mentioned to me the trouble they were having with getting multiple rev H chips to work on a Vs. System.  I don't know of a reason it wouldn't and don't have my test rig set up at the moment.  None of those minor revision things should cause an issue with Vs. games.  I should just set up my test rig and try it out.

		

